    "description": "<strong>WARBOUND</strong> 将策略卡组构建与史诗般的王国征服相结合，带来引人入胜的RTS体验。建造您的基地，组建战斗卡组，率领强大的军队，在动态实时战争中征服敌对王国。每一个决定都将左右您的王国命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3d81b37aed61a3dfbc6fd0bf14f232a4.poster.avif?t=1771864936\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3d81b37aed61a3dfbc6fd0bf14f232a4.webm?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3d81b37aed61a3dfbc6fd0bf14f232a4.mp4?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><br><strong>动态卡组构建</strong>：收集并制作强大的军队卡牌和药水卡牌，打造终极卡组。慎重选择您的卡牌——每场战斗都是对您策略与技巧的考验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/8ae3e021083ca2c8557898c8aaadcdec.poster.avif?t=1771864936\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/8ae3e021083ca2c8557898c8aaadcdec.webm?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/8ae3e021083ca2c8557898c8aaadcdec.mp4?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>史诗王国征服</strong>：在多样的地形中侵略敌对王国。制定策略，部署国王，在激烈的实时战斗中击溃敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/fe99c3c6589985e27120af0292a1fe9b.poster.avif?t=1771864936\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/fe99c3c6589985e27120af0292a1fe9b.webm?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/fe99c3c6589985e27120af0292a1fe9b.mp4?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多样化战斗卡牌</strong>：解锁从剑士到龙，从火球到旋风的众多军队和法术卡牌。每张卡牌都为您的卡组带来独特的力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3f3b8aa0ae0905cf955449dd1de3c192.poster.avif?t=1771864936\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3f3b8aa0ae0905cf955449dd1de3c192.webm?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/3f3b8aa0ae0905cf955449dd1de3c192.mp4?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>实时基地建设</strong>：通过建造重要建筑来扩展您的王国，这些建筑可产生资源并提供防御。在准备抵御无尽侵略的同时平衡经济。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/9e9465e1e46fc4db218fc1a2e1ffc412.poster.avif?t=1771864936\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/9e9465e1e46fc4db218fc1a2e1ffc412.webm?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119640/extras/9e9465e1e46fc4db218fc1a2e1ffc412.mp4?t=1771864936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WARBOUND</strong> 将让您在与强大对手的对抗中保持紧张，争取至高无上的地位。<strong>您会带领您的王国走向荣耀，还是会被敌人摧毁？</strong>",
